title: Provided further that such fungible compensatory area for rehabilitation component shall not be used for free sale component and shall be used to give additional area over and above eligible area to the existing tenants/occupants
clause_text: Provided further that such fungible compensatory area for rehabilitation component shall not be used for free sale component and shall be used to give additional area over and above eligible area to the existing tenants/occupants. Fungible compensatory area admissible to one rehabilitation tenement cannot be utilized for another rehabilitation tenement.
